{
  "stem": "3952.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A little-- And I would wash them without detergents, with-- with-- with-- with soil, with sand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was sand and water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I would work very hard to clean them, because the fat wouldn't come off if you didn't have some-- some detergent.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this lageralteste sympathized me because I spoke English, so he spoke to me as a [NON-ENGLISH] coming from a good house, and what have you studied?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a little schmooze with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, I come, and I go back to the [NON-ENGLISH], to the shoemaker, to this lagerkommandant, to the SS man.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I come back, and he calls me out from the line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stay in line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before-- before the block was-- was-- there was a ditch, kind of, going down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to run down that ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the lageralteste saw me in-- in that line, where he kept the people who he's going to beat up because of the shoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he came behind me, and gave me with his foot, gave me a-- a-- a shtoop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Gave me a push.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, [SPEAKS GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Run, because he's going to kill you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Fischer, give him a push.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SPEAKS GERMAN] Fischer was the blockalteste who was responsible for the clothing, for the-- for the store, for the shoes that he kept-- that he kept the-- the staff.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was staff sergeant, kind of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this Fischer throw me a pair of shoes, and I throw him one shoe, and I throw the other shoe, and I run out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this guy is running after me, but he is old, like 50, 50 years probably, or 40 years, and I was a 17-year-old, very fast boy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I ran around from one block to the other and came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
